sse. Bien plus qu’une collection, il s’agit donc d’une véritable « encyclopédie de la pensée moderne ».  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aLibrariesxSpecial collectionszQuébec (Province)xRare booksvCatalogs. 0aRare booksxCatalogs. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / General.2bisacsh1 aAudy-Trottier, Andréane, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aGladu, Kim, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311127214608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2022z978311127419540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782763757940?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763757940423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763757940/original  a978-3-11-127214-6  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-127419-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2022b2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles